---
title: Yellow Thai Style Peanut Veggie Noodles with Bell Pepper and Tenderstem® Broccoli
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Yellow Thai Style Peanut Veggie Noodles in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R17_W45_UK_V16043-3_Main_low-4975d933.jpg
